<h1 class="entry-title">Piracy Police Chief Calls For State Interference to Stop Internet Anarchy</h1>
</a>
<ul class="entry-meta">
<li class="entry-meta-item entry-meta-pubdate">On: <time class="published" datetime="2014-09-27T22:48:21+00:00" pubdate>28/09/2014</time></li>
<li class="entry-meta-item entry-meta-comments">Comments: <a href="http://torrentfreak.com/piracy-police-chief-calls-for-state-interference-to-stop-internet-anarchy-140928/#disqus_thread" data-disqus-identifier="94290 http://torrentfreak.com/?p=94290" class="comment-count-num">37</a></li>
